1
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:10,700
Have you ever heard about that

2
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,580
the cliff of a snow mountain

3
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:19,220
once fascinated numerous people?

4
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:24,140
Legend has it that,

5
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,940
there were treasures at the peak

6
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:32,860
but also there was a bottomless chasm hidden over there.

7
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:37,900
The smart, the fool

8
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:40,740
and the kind people,

9
00:00:41,380 --> 00:00:47,220
all are familiar to you.

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,660
On the mountainside, on the cliff,

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,580
on the cloud,

12
00:00:54,980 --> 00:01:00,100
and in the human world,

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:19,220
snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly.

14
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,980
Joy of Life Season 1

15
00:01:34,980 --> 00:01:37,900
Episode 31

16
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:42,040
Do you want to see me?

17
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:48,000
What's up?

18
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,800
What is Lin Wan'er

19
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:51,000
to you?

20
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,190
A wife-to-be.

21
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,040
Do you want to marry her

22
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:56,270
for Neiku

23
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:57,870
or for herself?

24
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,270
Even if she's a maidservant

25
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,310
or a slave girl,

26
00:02:00,630 --> 00:02:01,720
I'll marry nobody but her.

27
00:02:03,550 --> 00:02:06,310
So you really fall in love with her.

28
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,550
Are you holding the program

29
00:02:09,830 --> 00:02:10,630
of "Agony Father"

30
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:11,630
in the middle of the night?

31
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:12,750
The Princess Royal

32
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:14,470
has been kneeling outside the Imperial Study

33
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:16,080
for quite a while.

34
00:02:16,390 --> 00:02:17,080
How do you know about

35
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,160
what's happening in the palace?

36
00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:19,190
That's not the point.

37
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:23,110
The point is what you should do.

38
00:02:24,270 --> 00:02:25,390
I'd make it up with a kick.

39
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,910
Since the result is already clear,

40
00:02:29,670 --> 00:02:31,190
why don't you be generous

41
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,000
and intercede for her?

42
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,190
Intercede for her?

43
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:40,910
We should have mercy.

44
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,600
Don't be too ruthless.

45
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,390
Don't drive her too hard.

46
00:02:46,030 --> 00:02:48,440
Insidious as she is,

47
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:52,190
Li Yunrui has a lot of loyal followers as well.

48
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,240
If you shall have a foothold on the imperial court,

49
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,800
you must learn

50
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:59,190
the tactic of hardness and softness
to turn enemies into friends.

51
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:02,750
She tried to kill me!

52
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,240
Fan Xian,

53
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:12,000
have you ever considered

54
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,960
how Lin Wan'er will feel?

55
00:03:15,110 --> 00:03:16,080
Don't forget

56
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,960
Li Yunrui is her biological mother after all.

57
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:22,360
You beat Li Yunrui in this round.

58
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:23,880
What next?

59
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,960
You want to drive her up to the wall.

60
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,960
How would Lin Wan'er think about it?!

61
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,910
If you plan

62
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,830
to get married in future,

63
00:03:34,670 --> 00:03:37,800
will you get estranged because of this?

64
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,670
Fan Xian,

65
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:46,550
if you're sincere to her,

66
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:50,470
why can't you yield for her?

67
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,520
Allow me to think about it.

68
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,470
Tonight is the only chance

69
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,390
to intercede if you want.

70
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:39,070
Auntie,

71
00:04:39,670 --> 00:04:40,640
it's wide spread that

72
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,720
you are on my side.

73
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,880
I am!

74
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:45,670
If really so,

75
00:04:46,230 --> 00:04:48,230
why don't I have visibility

76
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:49,600
when you bribed Zhu Ge and contacted Zhuang Mohan?!

77
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,550
If you know all these,

78
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,510
it would be two people

79
00:04:56,110 --> 00:04:57,390
kneeling here now.

80
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,110
Now I have to kneel anyhow!

81
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:04,510
Please allow me to meet His Majesty!

82
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,200
Your Highness,

83
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:11,160
it's not good for you

84
00:05:12,270 --> 00:05:13,510
to kneel with me now.

85
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,790
Your Highness,

86
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,350
His Majesty asks you to come in.

87
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:40,350
Auntie is physically weak.

88
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,390
Please have mercy on her, Your Majesty!

89
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,480
No one else dares to

90
00:05:44,550 --> 00:05:46,230
intercede for her other than you.

91
00:05:46,350 --> 00:05:47,670
Do you know why?

92
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,790
They are afraid to get implicated.

93
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,790
Aren't you afraid?

94
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:54,440
I can't bear to see her get punished.

95
00:05:54,670 --> 00:05:56,760
Softhearted princes in history

96
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,110
came to no good end.

97
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,790
Your Majesty,

98
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:02,320
please have mercy on Auntie.

99
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:04,070
Let's wait a bit more.

100
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,830
For what?

101
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,510
Let's see

102
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,070
if anyone else will intercede for her.

103
00:06:14,790 --> 00:06:16,440
Possibly nobody dares to

104
00:06:17,830 --> 00:06:19,480
as it has come to this point.

105
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,640
Not necessarily.

106
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:22,000
Your Majesty,

107
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:23,830
Fan Xian, Chief Musician of the Court of Imperial Sacrifices,

108
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:25,550
requests for a meeting.

109
00:06:25,550 --> 00:06:26,110
Let him in.

110
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:33,950
It's such a surprise that

111
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,760
you are here.

112
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,440
Are you here to intercede?

113
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,920
If it weren't for someone else's reminder,

114
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,600
I'd almost forget how Wan'er feels.

115
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,390
They are after all mother and daughter

116
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:09,440
no matter how much hostility

117
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,350
between them.

118
00:07:11,550 --> 00:07:12,200
So...

119
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,600
To be honest,

120
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,720
it's a bit dis-organized in my mind.

121
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:18,920
So I found a place

122
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,830
and spent some time sitting there

123
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,160
to straighten it out.

124
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,720
Then I rushed here.

125
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:26,880
It's not too late anyway.

126
00:07:27,670 --> 00:07:29,510
You are here to intercede for her?

127
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:41,200
I, Fan Xian,

128
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:44,320
sincerely beg Your Majesty not to have mercy

129
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,790
and punish Li Yunrui by the most severe means!

130
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:57,790
Rise!

131
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,230
You don't enjoy kneeling.

132
00:08:00,550 --> 00:08:01,950
If you are really here to intercede,

133
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,880
I'd be very disappointed.

134
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:07,600
The Investigator's Office

135
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,880
and the power of the Neiku

136
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:12,550
can only be handed over to someone who can hold
their ground however much pressure they have.

137
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,070
I didn't think that much.

138
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:20,350
I'm curious about

139
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:23,320
how you changed your mind.

140
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,070
As I said,

141
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,670
I found a place

142
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,320
and spent some time straightening it out.

143
00:08:29,790 --> 00:08:30,950
Where is the place?

144
00:08:33,220 --> 00:08:38,980
=Tomb of my deceased husband, Teng Zijing=

145
00:08:43,910 --> 00:08:45,350
Now I'm leaving.

146
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,470
Thank you for helping me in the cooperation.

147
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:47,350
No need to thank me.

148
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,320
Someone wanted to get rid of you

149
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,520
by using the Investigator's Office.

150
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,150
Who?

151
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:51,960
We're still investigating.

152
00:08:54,110 --> 00:08:55,350
When I arrive in the capital city,

153
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,520
I can figure it out for sure.

154
00:08:57,110 --> 00:08:58,320
The one behind the assassination
attempt is extremely powerful

155
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,670
now that it even dared to do it in public.

156
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:01,960
If you stay,

157
00:09:02,350 --> 00:09:03,790
this is just the beginning.

158
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:05,080
The road ahead

159
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:07,440
will be full of hazards.

160
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,550
In this case,

161
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:11,710
I'd never leave you alone in the capital city

162
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,710
where you may encounter

163
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,440
both open and covert attacks.

164
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:18,200
I stay

165
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:20,320
because I want to.

166
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,230
I won't regret

167
00:09:22,670 --> 00:09:24,030
even if I have to undergo the most severe trials

168
00:09:25,150 --> 00:09:26,520
and lose my life.

169
00:09:34,590 --> 00:09:35,670
If Li Yunrui

170
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,880
only works against me,

171
00:09:37,470 --> 00:09:40,150
I'd yield for Wan'er.

172
00:09:41,110 --> 00:09:43,030
It's not easy to meet someone you truly love

173
00:09:43,110 --> 00:09:44,350
in a life time.

174
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,550
But that's not the only point to consider.

175
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:49,030
She killed Teng Zijing.

176
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:51,150
There is no reason for me

177
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:52,350
to let her go!

178
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,440
If I'd interceded for her,

179
00:09:56,470 --> 00:09:57,590
how selfish will I be!

180
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,640
All for a house guard?

181
00:10:01,590 --> 00:10:03,080
No, it's for a human life.

182
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:08,520
You're not completely polished.

183
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:10,960
No one should be polished with
their judgement of right or wrong.

184
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,280
I'm afraid

185
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,880
no one will come to intercede for her.

186
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:23,790
Let her go!

187
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:26,710
Thank you, Your Majesty!

188
00:10:27,590 --> 00:10:29,000
Send her far away.

189
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,440
Your Majesty, where shall she go?

190
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:36,200
She's been in the capital city for so many years.

191
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,960
Xinyang is her fief.

192
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,280
She can go back there.

193
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,840
Your Majesty!

194
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,030
His Majesty wants you to leave the capital city

195
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:09,200
for Xinyang.

196
00:11:10,790 --> 00:11:12,440
Did Fan Xian come to intercede?

197
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:15,640
He came to throw a stone.

198
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,320
Fantastic!

199
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,640
I thought he came to intercede.

200
00:11:22,350 --> 00:11:24,110
I was quite worried about that.

201
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,470
Too much luggage.

202
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,280
We should start packing up.

203
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:37,910
Auntie,

204
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,110
maybe I can try it again.

205
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,400
His Majesty's mind is like an abyss.

206
00:11:44,150 --> 00:11:47,960
It can't be persuaded or guessed.

207
00:11:49,230 --> 00:11:51,760
Whatever happened, she is the Princess Royal.

208
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:54,440
She can't be sent to the Ministry of Penalty.

209
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,790
Sending her to Xinyang

210
00:11:58,110 --> 00:12:01,200
is already the most severe penalty.

211
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:04,080
She doesn't deserve to die.

212
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:05,760
Get out of the way!

213
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,590
Princess, please return!

214
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:02,470
Her Highness said she doesn't want to see you.

215
00:14:04,030 --> 00:14:05,030
I'll just wait here.

216
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:07,280
No matter how long you wait, Her Highness won't see you.

217
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:38,670
She doesn't want to leave.

218
00:14:43,710 --> 00:14:45,760
Shall you meet her?

219
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:04,030
Given her physical condition,

220
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:05,440
she will be seriously ill if she stands there for a night.

221
00:15:06,670 --> 00:15:08,880
She will leave if she can't persist.

222
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,960
Her Highness might be weak physically,

223
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:13,590
but her temper

224
00:15:13,910 --> 00:15:14,960
is just like that of Your Highness.

225
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:17,590
She won't leave

226
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:19,280
if she says so.

227
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:58,000
Come in!

228
00:16:28,590 --> 00:16:30,150
There is freshly made ginseng tea.

229
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:31,960
Take some to warm up.

230
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:51,910
Are the maids in the palace all gone?

231
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:54,710
They are seeking other means of living,

232
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:57,200
thinking that by changing new hosts,

233
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,350
they can stay in the capital city.

234
00:17:00,350 --> 00:17:01,470
It's not an easy thing.

235
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,550
It is far better than following me.

236
00:17:06,110 --> 00:17:07,590
It is only too indifferent.

237
00:17:10,470 --> 00:17:11,400
Kind-hearted people

238
00:17:12,830 --> 00:17:15,830
have been devoured in the palace.

239
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:17,680
This is not right!

240
00:17:22,590 --> 00:17:25,470
I shouldn't meet you now.

241
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:27,560
But since we have met,

242
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,230
I will leave a few words to you.

243
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,800
Now that I have lost,

244
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,310
you still come to see me.

245
00:17:42,230 --> 00:17:44,000
That's a leap into the abyss.

246
00:17:46,830 --> 00:17:48,040
In biological sense,

247
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:50,880
we are mother and daughter.

248
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:52,310
It justifies it.

249
00:17:53,190 --> 00:17:54,230
After tonight,

250
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:57,000
you should pretend that we don't know each other.

251
00:17:58,560 --> 00:18:01,800
Don't come to see me off tomorrow.

252
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:09,680
Have you betrayed Nanqing?

253
00:18:14,830 --> 00:18:17,950
Does it really matter at this moment?

254
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:18,950
If you're wronged,

255
00:18:19,470 --> 00:18:21,070
I'll intercede with His Majesty.

256
00:18:21,470 --> 00:18:22,800
Don't you understand the words

257
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,470
I just said?

258
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:29,590
So,

259
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,470
have you betrayed Nanqing?

260
00:18:33,470 --> 00:18:34,160
I have!

261
00:18:34,950 --> 00:18:37,160
What else do you want to ask?

262
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:45,680
Did you attempt to hurt Fan Xian?

263
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:46,560
I did!

264
00:18:50,230 --> 00:18:51,160
You clearly know

265
00:18:52,430 --> 00:18:53,880
he is my fiancÃ©.

266
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:54,430
Why?

267
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:57,230
Are you here to question me

268
00:18:57,950 --> 00:18:59,350
before I leave?

269
00:19:01,190 --> 00:19:02,280
You came to see me

270
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:04,950
just a few times

271
00:19:05,040 --> 00:19:06,110
ever since I was born.

272
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:10,680
I thought it must be very difficult for you

273
00:19:11,760 --> 00:19:13,350
and things would become better after I grow up.

274
00:19:14,350 --> 00:19:17,230
Later, I was taken out of the imperial harem

275
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,310
and suffered from severe illness.

276
00:19:20,070 --> 00:19:21,040
You never ever came to see me

277
00:19:21,040 --> 00:19:22,920
in the imperial residence.

278
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:24,920
When I was seriously ill,

279
00:19:25,590 --> 00:19:26,520
I always wondered

280
00:19:27,470 --> 00:19:28,230
whether you would come

281
00:19:29,470 --> 00:19:31,160
before I died.

282
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:33,160
Do you even

283
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:34,920
have me as a daughter

284
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:36,000
in your heart?

285
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:39,350
You sabotaged Fan Xian without hesitation

