A lot of officers from the Six Ministries

576
00:36:46,470 --> 00:36:48,040
submitted memorials to the throne

577
00:36:48,470 --> 00:36:49,630
the other day in the Imperial Study

578
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:51,600
about your leakage of information

579
00:36:51,600 --> 00:36:54,150
that led to the seizure of Yan Bingyun.

580
00:36:54,430 --> 00:36:58,040
They all required it to be thoroughly investigated.

581
00:36:58,630 --> 00:36:59,320
But it was leaked

582
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,430
by the Princess Royal.

583
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:03,710
Li Yunrui only admits colluding with Zhu Ge

584
00:37:04,520 --> 00:37:05,670
to gang up for personal interest.

585
00:37:06,190 --> 00:37:07,320
She never admits

586
00:37:07,670 --> 00:37:09,230
giving away Yan Bingyun.

587
00:37:11,430 --> 00:37:13,230
That's her trap.

588
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:16,910
What did His Majesty say?

589
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:19,120
He didn't say anything

590
00:37:19,430 --> 00:37:23,470
other than watching the mounting public indignation.

591
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:28,600
Uncle,

592
00:37:29,390 --> 00:37:30,470
I didn't do anything.

593
00:37:30,470 --> 00:37:31,520
I am wronged.

594
00:37:33,390 --> 00:37:34,600
The truth is not important.

595
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:36,760
Then what is important?

596
00:37:38,670 --> 00:37:40,040
Your attitude.

597
00:37:42,520 --> 00:37:43,840
I don't understand.

598
00:37:47,040 --> 00:37:48,320
I know a little bit

599
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:50,840
about His Majesty.

600
00:37:51,950 --> 00:37:53,560
If I don't make it wrong,

601
00:37:53,630 --> 00:37:56,280
he will reach out to you very soon.

602
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:59,280
Reach out to me? For what?

603
00:38:00,520 --> 00:38:02,230
Whatever he asks you to do,

604
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:03,710
don't promise him.

605
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,280
He is the emperor.

606
00:38:06,870 --> 00:38:08,430
How can I deny his requirement?!

607
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:10,520
He didn't make the decision on court.

608
00:38:10,950 --> 00:38:12,710
Naturally it will be determined in private.

609
00:38:14,040 --> 00:38:14,800
Fan Xian,

610
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:17,000
your wedding with Wan'er

611
00:38:17,670 --> 00:38:19,280
is under preparation.

612
00:38:19,430 --> 00:38:20,430
Once you're married,

613
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:23,080
I'll transfer you to the Ministry of Personnel.

614
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:25,430
So don't create any trouble

615
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:27,190
at this important point.

616
00:38:28,600 --> 00:38:30,000
If it's not a distinct order,

617
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,560
don't promise.

618
00:38:31,870 --> 00:38:33,040
If there should be any trouble,

619
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:34,760
put it on me.

620
00:38:34,950 --> 00:38:36,000
Is that even possible?

621
00:38:39,430 --> 00:38:44,150
The emperor and the officer are not
like the master and the servant.

622
00:38:45,710 --> 00:38:49,150
They are more like two chess players.

623
00:38:52,910 --> 00:38:55,040
You can lose any chess piece,

624
00:38:56,150 --> 00:39:00,710
but you also need to fight for the necessary.

625
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:03,150
You didn't do anything wrong in this.

626
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:05,150
Besides,

627
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:07,670
in view of your title as the Poetic Genius Fan,

628
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:10,120
even His Majesty

629
00:39:10,390 --> 00:39:11,670
doesn't have any way

630
00:39:11,670 --> 00:39:13,430
to force you on the court.

631
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:15,280
But how do you tell

632
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:17,080
His Majesty will find me in private

633
00:39:17,190 --> 00:39:18,390
to allow me to justify myself.

634
00:39:20,390 --> 00:39:21,760
His Majesty is most interested

635
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:24,360
in the fight between people

636
00:39:24,470 --> 00:39:25,870
and can handle like nothing.

637
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:29,430
In his view, you still need more testing.

638
00:39:29,710 --> 00:39:32,800
And now is better than never.

639
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:36,670
Your Excellency,

640
00:39:36,670 --> 00:39:38,560
Mr. Fan is summoned to meet His Majesty in palace.

641
00:39:39,670 --> 00:39:40,560
There it goes!

642
00:39:42,870 --> 00:39:43,800
Off you go!

643
00:39:44,870 --> 00:39:46,470
Remember what I said.

644
00:39:46,870 --> 00:39:48,280
No matter what you're requested,

645
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,760
don't promise

646
00:39:50,670 --> 00:39:52,040
unless you're clearly requested to with an imperial edict.

647
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:54,430
I'll have a try.

648
00:40:13,080 --> 00:40:14,000
Lucky!

649
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:15,800
Master Yuan,

650
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,600
I won again this time.

651
00:40:20,670 --> 00:40:21,870
There is still room left.

652
00:40:28,470 --> 00:40:29,870
My bad! My bad! My bad!

653
00:40:34,470 --> 00:40:35,910
It's OK now.

654
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,150
You won!

655
00:40:51,710 --> 00:40:54,560
Your Highness! Your Highness!

656
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:58,560
This is...

657
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:01,360
Your Excellency! Please take a seat.

658
00:41:02,560 --> 00:41:03,430
This side please.

659
00:41:05,710 --> 00:41:07,430
What's going on?

660
00:41:08,230 --> 00:41:09,670
I don't know either.

661
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:13,230
His Majesty summoned us

662
00:41:13,230 --> 00:41:14,670
and didn't tell us why.

663
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:17,150
It's hard to tell if it's good or bad.

664
00:41:18,430 --> 00:41:21,320
His Majesty's will is deep and unpredictable.

665
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:24,430
Don't even try to guess His Majesty's will.

666
00:41:26,120 --> 00:41:28,230
Your Highness is reasonable and loyal

667
00:41:28,630 --> 00:41:31,560
which is very admiring.

668
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:33,470
What do you think?

669
00:41:33,670 --> 00:41:35,120
It's a contest between Your Highnesses.

670
00:41:35,390 --> 00:41:36,430
I'd rather stay impartial.

671
00:41:38,390 --> 00:41:39,840
Only you

672
00:41:39,840 --> 00:41:41,000
dare to say anything you want.

673
00:42:20,470 --> 00:42:22,470
Your Majesty, everyone is here.

674
00:42:22,670 --> 00:42:24,000
We can start the meal.

675
00:42:34,670 --> 00:42:35,950
This is a family meal.

676
00:42:36,630 --> 00:42:39,470
Help yourselves!

677
00:42:43,470 --> 00:42:44,230
Your Majesty,

678
00:42:45,040 --> 00:42:46,230
since it's a family meal,

679
00:42:46,390 --> 00:42:47,760
my presence is improper.

680
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:49,560
You're thick-skinned. It's alright!

681
00:42:51,080 --> 00:42:51,870
Go ahead with it!

682
00:43:18,180 --> 00:43:21,500
In the river of history,

683
00:43:21,780 --> 00:43:24,700
time goes round and round.

684
00:43:28,060 --> 00:43:31,060
Memories about the former and present lives

685
00:43:31,420 --> 00:43:34,940
join each other in an endless way.

686
00:43:37,380 --> 00:43:39,540
In the long drunken Milky Way,

687
00:43:40,020 --> 00:43:42,260
one season follows another in a flash,

688
00:43:42,260 --> 00:43:44,460
and the wild geese are flying south.

689
00:43:44,780 --> 00:43:46,380
I just can't give up

690
00:43:46,380 --> 00:43:49,380
to be with you for my whole life.

691
00:43:49,740 --> 00:43:54,660
I have been hovering in the dreams
for hundreds and thousands of times.

692
00:43:56,460 --> 00:43:58,460
I can't even say a word when I watch the flowers falling.

693
00:43:59,300 --> 00:44:01,340
Year after year in the wandering,

694
00:44:01,340 --> 00:44:03,900
I count the remaining years.

695
00:44:04,020 --> 00:44:06,100
Even though we can't meet each other anymore,

696
00:44:06,220 --> 00:44:07,660
