697
00:44:08,500 --> 00:44:10,340
I never feel regretful.

698
00:44:10,940 --> 00:44:12,300
In such a chaotic world,

699
00:44:12,300 --> 00:44:15,060
I still miss you as ever.

700
00:44:15,300 --> 00:44:17,700
I can't fall asleep under the moon.

701
00:44:18,540 --> 00:44:20,420
With a gentle heart,

702
00:44:20,620 --> 00:44:22,980
I cherish our remaining years.

